import React from 'react'

const ListQuestion = (l,onDelete) => {
   
  return (
    <>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
        <th> {l.prop.questionId}</th>
      <th scope="row">{l.prop.questionDetail}</th>
     
      
      <button className='btn btn-warning'>edit</button>
     <button className='btn btn-success' onClick={()=>onDelete()}>delete</button>
     
    </tr>
    </tbody>
    
    </>
  )
}

export default ListQuestion
